      <title>费尔巴哈提纲的第二条</title>
      <link>https://bigshans.github.io/post/%E8%B4%B9%E5%B0%94%E5%B7%B4%E5%93%88%E6%8F%90%E7%BA%B2%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%9D%A1/</link>
